                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">WILLIAMS</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18740112-99-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18740112-99-verdict-2" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18740112-99-verdict-2" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.—<hi rend="italic">He also</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">to having been before convicted at this Court in December</hi>, 1865, <hi rend="italic">
and had then been previously con<lb></lb>victed.—<rs id="t18740112-99-punishment-2" type="punishmentDescription">
